      <title>Hexo优化</title>
      <link href="/posts/41f.html"/>
      <url>/posts/41f.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="1-使用代理加快访问速度"><a href="#1-使用代理加快访问速度" class="headerlink" title="1.使用代理加快访问速度"></a>1.使用代理加快访问速度</h2><p>目前主流的静态网站托管网站一般有<a href="https://vercel.com/">Vercel</a>,<a href="https://www.netlify.com/">Netlify</a>.由于Vercel需要科学上网所以这里以Netlify为例</p><p>打开网站进入登录页面</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/bloega/beolgaimg@main/img/xxx.asjztmaf3mg.webp" alt=""></p><p>可以选择自己的账号登录，这里选择Github登陆后返回首页找到Add site导入自己的仓库</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/bloega/beolgaimg@main/img/beo.5yqx1eg9xtc0.webp" alt="image-20221220084547191" style="zoom: 80%;" /></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/bloega/beolgaimg@main/img/beoimgimage.1ciyqeodqtts.webp" alt="image-20221220085018745" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/bloega/beolgaimg@main/img/beoimgimage.38euaglbqrk0.webp" alt="image-20221220085258585" style="zoom: 33%;" /></p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/bloega/beolgaimg@main/img/beoimgimage.2ray5za8ysm0.webp" alt="image-20221220085509129" style="zoom: 33%;" /></p><p>等待构建完成</p><p><img src="https://cdn.staticaly.com/gh/bloega/beolgaimg@main/img/beoimgimage.ulmqqbyn34g.webp" alt="image-20221220085655666"></p><p>这里的网址是可以访问的，至此你的访问速度就快到飞起啦</p><h2 id="2-使用cdn加快图片加载"><a href="#2-使用cdn加快图片加载" class="headerlink" title="2.使用cdn加快图片加载"></a>2.使用cdn加快图片加载</h2><details ><summary> [bulue] 查看教程 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <h3 id="安知鱼-https-anzhiy-cn-posts-fe76-html"><a href="#安知鱼-https-anzhiy-cn-posts-fe76-html" class="headerlink" title="安知鱼 https://anzhiy.cn/posts/fe76.html"></a>安知鱼 <a href="https://anzhiy.cn/posts/fe76.html">https://anzhiy.cn/posts/fe76.html</a></h3>              </div>            </details><p>国内可以用的cdn</p><p><a href="https://www.jsdelivr.com/">jsdelivr CDN</a></p><p><a href="https://statically.io/">Statically CDN</a></p><p><a href="https://unpkg.com/">unpkeg</a></p><p>用法</p><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#jsdelivr</span></span><br><span class="line">https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/用户名/仓库地址@根目录/file</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#statically</span></span><br><span class="line">https://cdn.statically.io/gh/:user/:repo/:tag/:file</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#unpkg</span></span><br><span class="line">unpkg.com/:package@:version/:file</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="3-使用gulp压缩文件加快加载"><a href="#3-使用gulp压缩文件加快加载" class="headerlink" title="3.使用gulp压缩文件加快加载"></a>3.使用gulp压缩文件加快加载</h2><details ><summary> 查看教程 </summary>              <div class='content'>              <h3 id="Akilar-https-akilar-top-posts-49b73b87"><a href="#Akilar-https-akilar-top-posts-49b73b87" class="headerlink" title="Akilar https://akilar.top/posts/49b73b87/"></a>Akilar <a href="https://akilar.top/posts/49b73b87/">https://akilar.top/posts/49b73b87/</a></h3>              </div>            </details><p>1.全局安装gulp</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install gulp -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>2.安装模块</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install gulp-htmlclean gulp-htmlmin gulp-minify-css gulp-uglify gulp-imagemin --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>3.安装hexo-minifier </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-all-minifier --save</span><br><span class="line">或</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-all-minifier --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>然后在_config.butterfly.yml中添加</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">all_minifier:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">image_minifier:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">interlaced:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">multipass:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">optimizationLevel:</span> <span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">pngquant:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">progressive:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">silent:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">css_minifier:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">silent:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">exclude:</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;*.min.css&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">js_minifier:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">mangle:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">silent:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">output:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">compress:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">exclude:</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;*.min.js&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安装完成后运行hexo g输出如下</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: img/friend_404.gif [ 17.91% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007144906117.png [ 41.80% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007150608159.png [ 11.70% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: img/wechat.jpg [ 44.90% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: img/404.jpg [ 24.24% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007150612040.png [ 7.05% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007140654908.png [ 37.24% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007140547358.png [ 42.74% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007141320641.png [ 37.90% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007141211438.png [ 39.22% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007143951531.png [ 32.29% saved]</span><br><span class="line">INFO  update Optimize IMG: posts/c/image-20221007141745341.png [ 6.06% saved]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至此hexo的优化就完成了</p>]]></content>
      
      
